Returns an iterator of `u16` over the string encoded as UTF-16.

# Examples

```
let text = "Zażółć gęślą jaźń";

let utf8_len = text.len();
let utf16_len = text.encode_utf16().count();

assert!(utf16_len <= utf8_len);
```
